{"tid":368889,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[李氏力牆] 天文台考慮黃昏改發3號風球","createTime":"2017-08-22T01:10:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-24T05:59:10.000Z","uid":77196,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"edc154b9cce02fd3202d8b59e41dcc28d8853aae","tid":368889,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T01:10:41.000Z","msg":"一號戒備訊號現正生效，天文台表示，會在今日黃昏考慮改發3號強風訊號。<br />\n<br />\n天文台表示，上午9時，熱帶風暴天鴿集結在香港之東南偏東約650公里，預料向西北偏西移動，時速約25公里，移向廣東沿岸，並逐漸增強。<br />\n<br />\n天文台指，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>天鴿今早穩定地採取較為偏西路徑橫過呂宋海峽。按照現時預測路徑，天鴿會於明日(23日)早上最接近香港，並可能在本港100公里範圍內掠過</strong></span>。隨着天鴿靠近廣東沿岸，今晚及明早風力將會顯著增強，天氣轉壞，有狂風大驟雨，海面有大浪及湧浪，明早低窪地區可能出現水浸，市民應盡早做好所有防風防水浸措施。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/1637977/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F1637977%2F&d=Yugg0IjEz993OydPS6WIcO9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=1d765f57\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/1637977/</a>"},{"pid":"e238f22fb08e7ce55eac6a6336dba746a8a87a24","tid":368889,"uid":58031,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T01:30:29.000Z","msg":"10點左右掛八號，聽日6點半轉返三號<br />\n掂晒"},{"pid":"79ac75d25e05713f0455b54841362aabb1cfee36","tid":368889,"uid":68746,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T01:35:18.000Z","msg":"每個風都好有靈性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b168783ebcfba9f8b4d7249ef082d0924b0b6e6c","tid":368889,"uid":98386,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T01:37:27.000Z","msg":"屌你老母打風都咁撚熱"},{"pid":"08fbedb6aea0bc163cb4aef53d4cb760b42b5f3c","tid":368889,"uid":65756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T01:39:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你老母打風都咁撚熱</blockquote><br />\n唔洗出門口已經熱到仆街"},{"pid":"535cc901120b5960e6f3b2b27a820608211e0bd0","tid":368889,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT